high_descs: Turn around and walk to the other side of the island and face the white bowl and tomato.
Pick up the white bowl from the island.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the bowl inside the fridge, close the door and let the bowl chill for a few seconds, take the bowl out of the fridge and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the shelf in the right corner of the room.
Place the bowl on the second shelf to the right of the plate.
anns.task_desc: To chill a bowl and place it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around to your left walk straight, then turn left face the table of your left
Pick up the bowl at the edge of the table
Turn to your right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the fridge
Turn around to your right walk straight,turn left then head to the shelf rack
Put the bowl on the shelf rack
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl on the shelf rack

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table in the center of the room.
Pick up the mixing bowl on the table.
Place the bowl in the fridge, wait, and remove the bowl.
Turn around and walk to the the brown shelves in the corner
Place the bowl on the brown shelves.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl on the brown shelves in the corner of the room.
